definitions: a person or thing that injects something.
shortDefinitions: person or thing that injects something

definitions: (in an internal combustion engine) the nozzle and valve through which fuel is sprayed into a combustion chamber.
shortDefinitions: (in internal combustion engine) nozzle and valve through which fuel is sprayed into combustion chamber

definitions: (in a steam engine) a system of nozzles that uses steam to inject water into a pressurized boiler.
shortDefinitions: (in steam engine) system of nozzles that uses steam to inject water into pressurized boiler
